Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}大地と大空は 何故別れたのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}世界は残酷で されど美しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}石を投げる者と 投げられる者には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}容易に越えられぬ 柵がある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}立ち位置が替われば 正義は牙を剥く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}檻の中で吼えているのは 果たしてどちらか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:23:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}心臓を捧げた 戻せない黄昏に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}進み続けた夜の果て 楽園は何処にある？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}Requiem Requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}この夜に散った名も無き花よ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs18\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&\i1}どうか安らかに暁に眠れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们已经没有利用价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看看上面吧 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连和克里斯塔在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们不自首被抓的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}调查兵就会被全员处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我拜托皮克希斯司令一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要是那个时刻来临的话… 届时 我只能旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要做出选择的是你 还有他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}答复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}马车还真多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}到底怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在正集合所有兵团干部去城里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}进行解散调查军团的程序呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你看 那是执行那个团长死刑的处刑台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在应该正在执行最后的审判中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}失去调查军团亦即失去人类之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不是在敌人逼近时守护自身的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而是能够主动排除威胁的矛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}假设就在现在这个时刻敌人攻破罗塞之墙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:03:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}罗塞之墙的平民就会再度进入席纳之墙内避难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因早先的避难行动 储粮已经见底撑不了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}用不了多久 几乎所有平民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}都会被迫为生存而抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这意味着以罗塞之墙和席纳之墙为界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}分成两边的人类将开启内战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就算墙壁没被攻破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}罗塞之墙区域内也已渐有粮食不足问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}攻破席纳之墙的不是巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而是罗塞之墙平民的可能性并非是零
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}夺回玛利亚之墙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}走投无路的人类要开拓未来只有这个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你想说为此调查军团是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}领头杀入敌人阵地是我们调查军团的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一味被动防守是解决不了任何问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还是说各位有改变现况的妙计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾尔文 你似乎还没理解状况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你之所以会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}既不是为了讨论城墙的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也不是只因为杀人这种单纯的犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而是因为根据人类宪章第六条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}“将个人利益置于人类续存之上”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你严重违反此规条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没错 多次拒绝交出艾连·叶卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}已经完全违背人类宪章条款
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连是夺回码利亚之墙的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}做出决定的不是调查军团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连·叶卡是拥有未知力量的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要让他待在墙内必须背负相当程度的风险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么可能让区区一介军团长自行管理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但你对自己的主张十分坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}自导自演诱使事件把艾连·叶卡藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还对迪墨·利布斯杀人灭口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这已构成反叛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在你们才是人类真正的威胁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}皮克希斯司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}驻扎军团和调查军团同在前线拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}据说关系相当密切是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真遗憾您以为我们会与调查军团同一阵线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没有什么比人类自相残杀更愚蠢的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一旦在这狭隘的人世点了火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}相信要不了多久就会化为一片焦土了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}先前托洛斯特区保卫战时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我也这么教育士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}令他们自愿牺性奉献
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}若是调查军团会成为火种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那么就应该趁早捻熄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:06:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}毕竟被巨人攻破城墙之际要是没剩多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我看巨人也会很失望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}很好 那么进行商议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}陛下 您看怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾尔文 你打算就这样结束吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那么以陛下之名宣布判决
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}受刑人 艾尔文·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}以违反人类宪章第六条之罪处以死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}此判决即刻执行 带下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这样真的好吗 艾尔文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你真的就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}罗塞之墙被攻破了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}突然出现的超大型巨人和盔甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}破坏了卡拉涅斯区的两扇大门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在从东区方向有大量难民涌入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}确保避难路线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}驻扎军团前线部队全兵力在东区集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}引导平民至席纳之墙避难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}快点行动 以平民避难为最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:07:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}封闭席纳之墙全区大门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不准让任何难民闯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那 那是指要对罗塞之墙的平民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}对超过半数的人类见死不救的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就跟刚才他说的一样只会引发内战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有可能会瘫痪中央政府机能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要真如此一切就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但 但是那也只是假设而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}重点在假设有可能成真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们可是有最高决定权的机关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还不决点照做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可恶 没想到城墙会在这种时候被攻破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但也算是不幸中的大幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}已经找到“力量”了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只要撑到“容器”接受力量为止就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没错 现在不是为眼前的损失慌乱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只要还有席纳之墙总有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}啊啊 只要雷斯卿回来就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}只能做了 去把门堵上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}再等就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}做出选择的会是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}谁来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还愣着干什么快点行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是想背叛王政府吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我是罗塞之墙的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我要阻止大门封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也算上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}达里斯·萨克雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}听到他们的判断您是否感到意外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}萨克雷总统
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}萨克雷 这到底
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}方才的通报是误报 请安心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在并没有确认到任何巨人来袭的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什…你这家伙这是想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}主谋者是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}中央宪兵大半都去了别的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}该说是走运吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}方才我说驻扎军团与调查军团无联手之事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可我忘了多说这一句
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们可也没和你们站同一阵线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}虽说我也与艾尔文有一样的想怯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但也曾犹豫是否将一切交给你们政府
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}才是真正对人类有益的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为你们大概比我们更加了解墙壁和巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}想着如果只有你们才能挽救更多人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那么就让艾尔文上处刑台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}当然 依情况我们也有从容就义的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但现在你们已经给出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}即便对巨人的力量和来龙去脉一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们仍能比你们令更多生命续存
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}别 别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就算镇压了这里那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你以为民众会服从吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}民众只会臣服于王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}地方贵族也不会默不作声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看样子你还没理解状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这不是威胁 是政变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}已完成中央宪兵镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}所谓的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}有时比起国王更会优先遵从长官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}既然这国王是假的就更不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们打算拥立真正的王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么会…居然打算做到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你以为这跟诈欺没两样的手段真行得通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果真的发生紧急状况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你们方才的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}才真的是违反人类宪章第六条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}再加上拥立伪王独自揽政之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}足以判处极刑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可恶你给我起来 臭老头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}住口你这个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾尔文 是你赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:12:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}奈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}人类不得不走上更艰难的荆棘之路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如信所述 政变成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}王都和行政区都由萨克雷总统临时接收
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}目前还没有传出贵族叛乱的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但是 那利布斯会长的事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为有证言说是冤罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}会长儿子的弗雷格尔正在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你还不懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}王政府的家伙们根本没打算救我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现在假装没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等真的被杀就来不及了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}下次再被巨人攻击就什么都不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不管是公司还是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}在那之前把真相写出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就跟这上面写的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}把枉加冤罪 王政府施加的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}弗利玆王其实是伪王都写清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}关于你们的事情也证明是正当防卫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也就是说 我们现在都是自由身了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}还真是夸张的豪赌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不过不只是艾尔文他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是每个人的选择 一起改变了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我害你托付给我的三位队员枉死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一部分的中央宪兵和宪兵的头头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:15:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连和希丝特莉亚都还在不知道在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}得决点找出来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那件事我有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}让这场战斗在那里画下句点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs16\an9\1c&H0080FF&}现在可以公开情报\N地下礼拜堂\N代代进行继承\N王家之力的神圣仪式的地方\N墙壁是由会自行发光的神秘矿石构成\N推测是由巨人之力做出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}公开宣布因艾尔文的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}现有体制已崩坏的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是在兵团组织压制王都与行政区后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}立刻在为了他所准备的处刑台上发表的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}正如方才萨克雷总统的宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们的目的不在以兵团组织进行统治
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}将由真正的王家取代弗利兹家拥立新王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}担任引导民众的明灯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这我了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:16:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但民众真会那么轻易接纳新王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}事实上确实有许多人都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不知道今后该相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}若是为了人类着想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}应该要照旧将一切托付给王政府
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}正如皮克希斯司令所言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}他们令人类在巨人威胁下生存的手段就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就算对半数人类见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也比全人类灭绝来得好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我本该交出艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}连同同伴和自己的性命一起放弃责任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}将一切托付给王政
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果说与个人比起来 人类更加尊贵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你的使命还是如此艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}看样子死了反而是种解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但 如果是这样你为何不那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:16:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要说说我的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}因为我从以前就看那些家伙不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}令人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}一脸跩样的家伙和明明不伟大却居上位的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不 不如说是因为我喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}仔细想想我一直都期待有这一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也就是说即使你没动手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我也打算在死前给他们一点颜色瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这场政变对人类是好是坏我一点兴趣也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我真是个大坏蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但说起这个 你也是一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你其实是不想死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}和我一样 比起人类的命运选择了个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我似乎太骄傲自大了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你的理由是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}该轮你回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}其实我有个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是从小就有的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}汉吉分队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你说有两人所在之处的线索是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我接下来就说明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是艾尔文交给我的雷斯卿领地的调查报告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}内容几乎都是关于五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}袭击雷斯家的那个事件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}没错 就是玛利亚之墙被破坏的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}总之 我从头概略说明起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}罗德·雷斯这个男人作为领主的评价并不差
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}膝下有五个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}别是长女芙莉妲个性随和颇受领民喜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但在五年前的夜晚 发生一场悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}盗贼趁着情势正混乱时袭击领地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}烧毁了村里唯一一座礼拜堂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可怜的是那天晚上雷斯一家都在那梼告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}除了当家罗德·雷斯以外的家族成员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}全都惨遭盗贼杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这是在希丝特莉亚的母亲被中央宪兵杀害前几天发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}也就是说罗德·雷斯在失去家人后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就立刻主动接触希丝特莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}从中可看出他们需要希丝特莉亚的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}血缘关系吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}你是想说关键在于血统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}这个部分现在还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}比起那个我在意的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}礼拜堂被全部烧毁这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}礼拜堂是石造建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}要破坏掉需要花费相当的时间跟力气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}真是盗贼的话 应该会偷完就立刻逃跑才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}而且看见盗贼的只有罗德·雷斯一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}之后他动用私产重建了礼拜堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}是为了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}不如说这里不可能和巨人无关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}就算只是我的贸然推测
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但可疑到这个程度 已值得去一探究竟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}等天一亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}兵团就会进到雷斯领地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}雷斯应该不会好心等到那时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}我们不赶快过去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连说不定会被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}能巨人化的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可以借由吃掉巨人来继承能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}如果这是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}艾连是什么时候 怎么变成巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}吃掉了谁才获得能力的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}希丝特莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}为了救出艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}米卡莎等人朝着礼拜堂前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}但被拘束的艾连得知了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}父亲古利夏不可原谅的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei}下一回“罪孽”

